{"id":985,"date":"2023-07-18T22:28:37","date_gmt":"2023-07-18T13:28:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/?post_type=artist&#038;p=985"},"modified":"2023-12-02T00:09:36","modified_gmt":"2023-12-01T15:09:36","slug":"taeyang","status":"publish","type":"artist","link":"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/?artist=taeyang","title":{"rendered":"TAEYANG"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>TAEYANG is a recording artist and one of the most reputable vocalists and performers of this century. From the time he dropped his debut single, \u2018Only Look At Me\u2019, off his first mini album, \u2018Hot\u2019, he successfully broke out as a solo artist with a powerful presence. Released a series of hits such as \u2018Wedding Dress\u2019 and \u2018I Need A Girl (Feat. G-Dragon)\u2019 that topped the major charts both in Korea and internationally, and led to him winning \u2018Best Male Singer\u2019 at the Mnet Asian Music Awards both in 2010 and 2014.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>His single, \u2018Eyes, Nose, Lips\u2019 became a smash hit and an instant classic, subsequently winning \u2018Song of the Year\u2019 on all major Korean award shows including the 2014 Mnet Asian Music Awards and the 2015 Golden Disc Awards. He participates in the songwriting and composition of his albums and has a profound understanding of various music genres including soul, pop and R&amp;B. He is recognized for his vocals as the lead singer for BIGBANG, one of the most influential and decorated acts in the history of K-Pop and one of the best-selling boy bands of all time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Recently, TAEYANG regrouped with BIGBANG to release \u2018Still Life\u2019, their first comeback in four years, which topped all of the major charts in Korea as well as going #1 on iTunes in 33 countries around the world.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With global success both as a member of BIGBANG and as a solo artist, TAEYANG continues to push the boundaries and expand his spectrum as an artist. His January 2023 release \u2018VIBE (feat. Jimin of BTS)\u2019 charted on the Billboard Hot 100 and signaled a grand return after a six-year hiatus. He subsequently dropped his comeback EP album \u2018Down to Earth\u2019 with \u2018Seed\u2019 and the smash global single, \u2018Shoong! (feat. LISA of BLACKPINK)\u2019.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>TAEYANG is a living legend who will continue to evolve and stay true to his artistry.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ty-main-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-942\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ty-main-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ty-main-200x300.jpg 200w, https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ty-main-768x1152.jpg 768w, https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ty-main-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/ty-main.jpg 1067w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links aligncenter is-layout-flex wp-block-social-links-is-layout-flex\"><li class=\"wp-social-link wp-social-link-instagram  wp-block-social-link\"><a rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/__youngbae__\/\" class=\"wp-block-social-link-anchor\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><path d=\"M12,4.622c2.403,0,2.688,0.009,3.637,0.052c0.877,0.04,1.354,0.187,1.671,0.31c0.42,0.163,0.72,0.358,1.03